message: Using the in-process token cache is deprecated as of the 4.2.0 release and may be removed in the 5.0.0 release or the 'O' development cycle. The in-process cache causes inconsistent results and high memory usage. When the feature is removed the auth_token middleware will not cache tokens by default which may result in performance issues. It is recommended to use  memcache for the auth_token token cache by setting the memcached_servers option.
